content.html: We saw a tweet recently that said ‘starting a job feels like you’re a new character on the ninth season of a tv show.’ If you’ve ever related to this, you’re not the only one! Starting a new job can bring up all sorts of feelings; excitement, doubt, joy, and fear to name a few.
